# Cursor Rules for Ticketing Microservices Project

## Git Commit Message Generation

When asked to generate a commit message, follow the workflow documented in `.cursor/workflows/generate-commit.md`.

## Common Commit Types

- `feat`: New feature
- `fix`: Bug fix
- `refactor`: Code refactoring
- `docs`: Documentation changes
- `style`: Code style changes
- `test`: Test changes
- `chore`: Maintenance tasks

## Project Structure

- `client/` - Next.js frontend
- `auth/`, `orders/`, `payments/`, `tickets/`, `expiration/` - Microservices
- `common/` - Shared package
- `infra/k8s/` - Kubernetes manifests
